ct"><p id="p-0001" num="0000">Disclosed herein are a hybrid analog to digital converter and a sensing apparatus using the same. The hybrid analog to digital converter includes: a continuous time modulator amplifying and outputting an analog differential signal; a discrete time modulator amplifying and outputting again the analog differential signal that is amplified and output by the continuous time modulator; and a comparator performing 1 bit ADC function of representing an analog signal output by the discrete time modulator to be High or Low.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>